[metadata]
Name:Howling Mine Tapped — No Extra Draw
Goal:Win
Turns:3
Difficulty:Easy
Description:Howling Mine ("At the beginning of each player's draw step, if Howling Mine is untapped, that player draws an additional card"). Here P0's Howling Mine is TAPPED, so the intervening-if condition (IsPresent$ Card.untapped, CR 603.4) is NOT met and the trigger must NOT fire on P1's draw step. P1 draws no extra card; P0 draws nothing either. Before the IsPresent$ untapped intervening-if was modeled, a tapped Howling Mine still wrongly granted the extra draw.

